VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT requests\.(get|post|put|delete|patch|head|request)\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:request\.GET|request\.POST|request\.args|request\.form|input\(|argv|\+ && MISSING:allowlist|whitelist|urlparse|ipaddress|is_private|validators\.url
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects HTTP requests made with user-supplied URL values that may enable SSRF.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for SSRF: requests Library with User-Controlled URL.
